<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Dear ALF III Investor,&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We&#8217;re proud to share that Viola Credit has suc=
cessfully completed the final close of the third series of Asset-Based Lend=
ing funds, ALF III (the &#8220;Fund&#8221;).&nbsp;The Fund raised over&nbsp=
;<b>$2.0 billion&nbsp;</b>of committed and investable capital (including
 related vehicles). This surpasses our original&nbsp;<b>$1.5 billion target=
</b>.</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We&#8217;re honored to receive the continued trust o=
f our longstanding partners, while also being greatly appreciative of the t=
rust placed in us by our new LPs. The Fund received commitments from a wide=
 range of global investors, including leading
 pension funds, insurance companies, financial institutions, investment con=
sultants, and global advisors.&nbsp;We believe this speaks to the value tha=
t our differentiated approach to asset-based lending within the innovation =
economy can bring to our LPs.</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">As the ABL landscape continues to evolve, we believe=
 ALF III will see a significant number of opportunities to partner with bes=
t-in-class FinTech and tech-enabled lenders.&nbsp;&nbsp;We will seek to sup=
port these originators as they expand, diversify
 their funding base, and give them access to scalable capital solutions.</p=
>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We would like to take this opportunity to also welco=
me&nbsp;Conor Sheehy&nbsp;to the Firm as&nbsp;the&nbsp;Head of ABL Europe, =
based in our London office. Conor brings over 20 years of experience in str=
uctured finance and warehouse lending, most recently leading
 the European Warehouse Finance business at HSBC Innovation Bank. Conor joi=
ns our established and growing global platform of over 40 professionals acr=
oss Viola Credit.
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We wanted to thank you for your trust and ongoing pa=
rtnership. We remain committed to delivering disciplined returns and long-t=
erm value to you, our valued partners.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Warm regards,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in">Ido Vigdor, Ruthi Furman=
, Alex Ginzburg&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in">On behalf of the entire&=
nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:0in">Viola Credit Management =
Team<o:p></o:p></p>
